layerGroup.name: bathymetry_AMP_grp
layerGroup.title: Bathymetry of Australian Marine Parks (AMPs)
layerGroup.abstractTxt:
Multibeam bathymetry data complied from various sources and compiled into a single Geotiff per Australian Marine Park (AMP). Each AMP Geotiff is gridded to the equivalent of the finest resolution of data available in that region and represents a multi-resolution mosaic.
This layer group comprises of bathymetry mosaics overlaid on derived hillshade, clipped to the boundaries of Australian Marine Parks (2025).
